3prx A 1101 C 1101

A redox-regulated disulphide may form between two units of Complement C5 at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.

3prx A 1159 C 1101

A redox-regulated disulphide may form between two units of Complement C5 at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.
